No!

52
00:03:08,870 --> 00:03:09,920
Pardon me?

53
00:03:10,420 --> 00:03:12,070
I love the Pony Tones.

54
00:03:12,310 --> 00:03:13,830
I'm one of their biggest fans.

55
00:03:14,180 --> 00:03:16,320
But I do not want to
perform with them.

56
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:18,180
Why not, Fluttershy?

57
00:03:18,530 --> 00:03:25,620
