waste of an exquisite talent,

70
00:03:53,650 --> 00:03:55,460
but I understand that
you're not comfortable.

71
00:03:56,210 --> 00:03:56,890
Thank you.

72
00:03:57,570 --> 00:03:58,780
Ooh! Angel's right!

73
00:03:58,940 --> 00:03:59,890
We better get going!

74
00:04:00,130 --> 00:04:02,710
