87
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,350
Whoo hoo! Yeah!

88
00:04:53,570 --> 00:04:55,160
Rarity, you were awesome!

89
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:59,130
Thank you, Spike, but
this is an ensemble.

90
