to find a deep voice

172
00:08:32,490 --> 00:08:34,050
to replace Big Mac's?

173
00:08:34,250 --> 00:08:36,330
<i>(chuckle)</i>

174
00:08:36,430 --> 00:08:39,600
Pardon me, Zecora,
but this is no laughing matter.

175
00:08:39,610 --> 00:08:41,830
