the harmonies to work!

176
00:08:41,900 --> 00:08:44,040
Without it, the
performance will be ruined!

177
00:08:44,170 --> 00:08:46,570
Please forgive my
strange elation,

178
00:08:46,670 --> 00:08:49,870
but I was not laughing
at your situation.

179
00:08:50,010 --> 00:08:50,780
Then what?

180
00:08:51,150 --> 00:08:54,430
Remember when you pony folk
stumbled into Poison Joke?

181
00:08:54,940 --> 00:08:57,930
<i>Miss Fluttershy had</i>
<i>an unusual change,</i>

182
00:08:58,060 --> 00:08:59,960
<i>deepening her vocal range.</i>

183
00:09:00,430 --> 00:09:02,290
(very low voice) I don't
want to talk about it.

184
00:09:04,150 --> 00:09:05,140
Yes, yes!

185
00:09:05,730 --> 00:09:08,260
