low, making it sound like...

186
00:09:09,150 --> 00:09:10,170
Flutterguy!

187
00:09:10,630 --> 00:09:12,860
With these leaves,
I can mix a brew

188
00:09:12,870 --> 00:09:15,410
creating the same
effect on you.

189
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:17,740
Zecora, that's fantastic!

190
00:09:17,860 --> 00:09:19,460
Yes! I'll do it!

191
00:09:19,640 --> 00:09:22,070
I'd do anything for the animals!

192
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:24,830
Why, you'd even
appear on stage!

193
00:09:25,300 --> 00:09:26,630
Oh, except that.

194
00:09:28,510 --> 00:09:30,710
I just can't bring
myself to sing on stage

195
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:32,070
in front of everypony.

196
00:09:33,630 --> 00:09:37,100
