204
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:57,050
<i>(squeaks)</i>

205
00:09:57,600 --> 00:10:02,540
Oh, OK, then...mix it up.

206
00:10:03,820 --> 00:10:10,300
♪

207
00:10:10,310 --> 00:10:12,530
Now do it just
like we practiced.

208
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:14,520
<i>(gasp)</i>

209
00:10:15,730 --> 00:10:24,400
<i>(crowd</i>
<i>chatters)</i>

210
00:10:24,410 --> 00:10:26,940
Good evening,
citizens of Ponyville!

211
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:29,350
I want to thank you all
for coming out tonight

212
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:32,240
and generously supporting
the Ponyville Pet Center!

213
00:10:32,830 --> 00:10:36,030
<i>Thanks to your kindness, pets</i>
<i>are finding loving homes</i>

214
00:10:36,070 --> 00:10:38,710
<i>and we are sure to meet</i>
<i>our fundraising goal!</i>

215
00:10:39,270 --> 00:10:40,270
